      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/googles-contemplated-mega-deal-would-prompt-new-fight-with-regulators-2024-04-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[谷歌母公司 Alphabet 擬收購行銷軟體公司 HubSpot 的計畫可能會引發監管機構的反對，儘管許多專家認為這不會抑制競爭，並且會要求這家科技巨頭在與反壟斷監管機構的鬥爭中開闢新戰線。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/googles-contemplated-mega-deal-would-prompt-new-fight-with-regulators-2024-04-08/</guid>
